This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Emanuel Wontorra

Project's homepage:          http://www.wontorra.net/staticpages/index.php?page=director

See the file COPYING for license information.

Description:
-----------
Director is a plugin to use the multifeed option of some Premiere channels(Direkt,Sport1,Sport2).

Requirements:
-------------
VDR >= 1.4.X
You need to apply the patch vdr-director.diff to vdr

Usage:
-----
Left  switches to the first mulifeed channel
Right switches to the last multifeed channel
Up	  switches one multifeed channel up
Down	switches one multifeed channel down
1...9		choose one of the first nine channels direct
0		toggle between the last two channels
OK		show/hide the OSD

Setup Option:
-------------

- Hide Mainmenu Entry: Hides the plugin main menu entry
- Swap up and down: Swaps the action on up and down keys
- Portal Mode: in portal mode the first multifeed channel has no number,
  introduced to match the Sport Portal option numbers
